OL,3,CFormer Arsenal goalkeeper Alex
OL,4,CManninger killed in road accident
OL,6,FFormer Arsenal goalkeeper Alex
OL,7,FManninger has been killed in a road
OL,8,Fincident, his first club Red Bull
OL,9,FSalzburg have announced.
OL,11,FThe Bundesliga outfit announced on
OL,12,FThursday that the 48-year-old had
OL,13,Fdied, in a post on its official X
OL,14,Faccount.
OL,16,FIt said: "We mourn our former
OL,17,Fgoalkeeper Alexander Manninger, who
OL,18,Ftragically lost his life in a traffic
OL,19,Faccident.
